room_title: Escape room "Miss Pearl's Parlour" by The Ville Escape Room in Kirksville
room_description: Miss Pearl was a very popular lady in the old west. You are the unfortunate gentleman who didn't pay for your stay. She's demanding all of the gold in your pockets but you don't have any. She's locked you away in her Parlour and is sending someone to settle the bill the old-fashioned way. You have 60 minutes to escape your fate. Can you find the key to escape?
